# Public GitHub Pages allowlist
#
# Ignore every file by default. Only the deployable website surface is
# explicitly allowed below. This keeps internal writing workflows, prompts,
# templates, research notes, and design-process files out of the public repo.
*

# Keep directories traversable so selected files can be allowed.
!*/

# Repository and GitHub Pages configuration
!.gitignore
!.nojekyll
!CNAME

# Website application
!index.html
!styles.css
!script.js

# Public article index and dated article content
!entries.json
!entries/[0-9][0-9][0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9]-[0-9][0-9].md

# Deterministic publication checks (no private prompts or source material)
!scripts/validate-daily-entry.mjs
!scripts/verify-site-publication.mjs
!scripts/recover-pages-publication.mjs

# Images actually referenced by the website
!assets/daily-thought-header.png
!assets/daily-thought-icon-small.webp
!assets/illustrations/about-vase.png
!assets/illustrations/hero-still-life.png
!assets/illustrations/method-sprig.png
